author: Eric Branch
title: Blindside bind? LT Staley misses second straight practice
text:
Photo: Scott Strazzante, The Chronicle Joe Staley, the 49ers’ Pro Bowl tackle, hurt his knee Sunday but didn’t miss a snap. This week, he’s missed two practices. Joe Staley, the 49ers’ Pro Bowl tackle, hurt his knee Sunday but...
As if Colin Kaepernick didn’t already have enough on his mind: His blindside protector, Pro Bowl left tackle Joe Staley , missed his second straight practice because of a knee injury.
